OL,3,CFamily of teenager who drowned warn of
OL,4,C'devastating' open water dangers
OL,6,FThe family of a 17-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied after getting into difficulty in
OL,8,Fa tarn in the Lake District have
OL,9,Fwarned of the "devastating
OL,10,Fconsequences" of entering open water
OL,11,Fas they paid tribute to his life.
OL,13,FAbsi Ahmed, from Poulton-le-Fylde in
OL,14,FLancashire, died at High Dam Tarn,
OL,15,Fnear Windermere, on 7 April.
OL,17,FIn a statement, his family remembered
OL,18,Fhim as a "loyal friend" and a "loving
OL,19,Fson" whose death has "shaken" the
OL,20,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
