CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777389066
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who drowned warn of
OL,4,C'devastating' open water dangers
OL,6,FPaying tribute to the teenager, his
OL,7,Ffamily said: "Absi was a bright, kind,
OL,8,Ffunny young man with his whole future
OL,9,Fahead of him.
OL,11,F"He was a loyal friend, a loving son,
OL,12,Fand someone who brought warmth and
OL,13,Flaughter wherever he went. His loss
OL,14,Fhas shaken our entire community."
OL,16,FAlongside their tribute, the family
OL,17,Fstated they wanted to highlight the
OL,18,Fextreme risks associated with open
OL,19,Fwater swimming.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
