PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777389066
OL,3,CFamily of teenager who drowned warn of
OL,4,C'devastating' open water dangers
OL,6,FThey are urging others to follow
OL,7,Fsafety advice provided by Cumbria Fire
OL,8,F& Rescue Service to prevent further
OL,9,Ftragedies, highlighting the "Float to
OL,10,FLive" technique:
OL,12,FA full inquest into Absi's death has
OL,13,Fbeen scheduled for 1 September.
OL,15,FA fundraising page set up by his
OL,16,Ffriends has raised almost #20,000 to
OL,17,Fsupport his parents and other causes
OL,18,Fclose to the family's hearts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
