OL,3,CFamily of teenager who drowned warn of
OL,4,C'devastating' open water dangers
OL,6,FIn a statement, his friends said: "We
OL,7,Fgrew up together, made memories we'll
OL,8,Fnever forget, and planned a future we
OL,9,Fthought we'd all be part of."
